Don't worry.

311
00:24:54,472 --> 00:24:57,270
If they come and collect the money,
I'm sure we'll get them.

312
00:24:57,475 --> 00:24:58,464
All this is talk,

313
00:24:58,610 --> 00:24:59,838
what we need is some real action.

314
00:25:11,689 --> 00:25:14,249
Something's up. Raymond's in trouble.

