I'm sure we'll get them.

323
00:25:36,915 --> 00:25:38,212
I understand your situation

324
00:25:38,483 --> 00:25:39,848
and I'll note it in the report.

325
00:25:40,151 --> 00:25:43,416
Good luck with the case.

326
00:25:52,263 --> 00:25:53,423
You come, too.

327
00:25:56,701 --> 00:25:58,032
Why the long face?

328
00:25:58,269 --> 00:25:59,258
Did you two have a fight?

329
00:25:59,971 --> 00:26:02,201
Right! But it's the last one.

330
00:26:16,621 --> 00:26:17,610
Yes? I'll get him.

331
00:26:17,655 --> 00:26:18,644
Hold this.

332
00:26:20,291 --> 00:26:22,282
Ka-kui, phone.

333
00:26:22,527 --> 00:26:23,516
Put it through.

334
00:26:24,429 --> 00:26:25,418
Right. Put it through.

335
00:26:28,099 --> 00:26:29,088
Hello. Ka-kui.

336
00:26:29,300 --> 00:26:30,699
May's been kidnapped!

337
00:26:31,035 --> 00:26:32,024
When?

338
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,469
We'd just left the shop

339
00:26:33,638 --> 00:26:35,196
and someone lifted her into a van.

340
00:26:35,473 --> 00:26:36,735
Who did it?

341
00:26:37,242 --> 00:26:40,302
I don't know. But it must be
something to do with you.

342
00:26:40,512 --> 00:26:42,412
Could it be those thugs again?

343
00:26:42,847 --> 00:26:44,576
Chu Tu.

344
00:26:45,450 --> 00:26:47,577
Ka-kui... Hello?

345
00:26:50,889 --> 00:26:51,878
Ka-kui! What's up?

346
00:26:51,923 --> 00:26:53,823
An old score.

347
00:26:54,259 --> 00:26:55,248
Ka-kui!

348
00:26:55,894 --> 00:26:56,883
What happened?

349
00:26:56,928 --> 00:26:57,917
May is caught.

350
00:26:58,663 --> 00:27:00,961
What's the matter?
Sign this cheque before you're dead.

351
00:27:00,999 --> 00:27:01,829
Our brothers...

352
00:27:01,866 --> 00:27:02,924
Please stop.
He's a patient.

353
00:27:02,967 --> 00:27:03,899
Let me finish.

354
00:27:03,935 --> 00:27:06,335
We did what you asked.
That's why we deserve something.

355
00:27:06,538 --> 00:27:07,937
You won't need
any money when you're dead.

356
00:27:22,820 --> 00:27:23,809
Chu Tu!

357
00:27:26,858 --> 00:27:27,847
Chu Tu! Hey, you!

358
00:28:04,996 --> 00:28:05,985
Chu Tu! Chu Tu!

359
00:28:10,568 --> 00:28:11,557
Where is May?

360
00:28:11,703 --> 00:28:12,692
I don't know.

361
00:28:12,804 --> 00:28:14,101
I didn't do anything. It's him.

362
00:28:16,841 --> 00:28:17,933
Where the hell's May?

363
00:28:19,377 --> 00:28:20,708
Stop it! He's sick.

364
00:28:21,212 --> 00:28:22,201
Put him down.

365
00:28:22,814 --> 00:28:24,372
Where did you take her?

366
00:28:24,616 --> 00:28:25,742
I didn't take her.

367
00:28:25,984 --> 00:28:26,973
Who did then?

368
00:28:27,018 --> 00:28:28,349
I was very nasty to you before.

369
00:28:28,553 --> 00:28:29,918
But now I'm sick and penniless.

370
00:28:30,221 --> 00:28:32,917
Why would I take her?

371
00:28:33,157 --> 00:28:34,954
He's got no money now.

372
00:28:35,159 --> 00:28:36,353
It has nothing to do with us.

373
00:28:36,694 --> 00:28:38,559
He made your life miserable.

374
00:28:38,730 --> 00:28:40,095
We did it because of money.

375
00:28:41,566 --> 00:28:42,555
Then who could it be?

376
00:28:45,436 --> 00:28:47,131
There's a phone over there.

377
00:28:48,106 --> 00:28:49,664
Don't die before you sign this!
Sign this cheque before you're dead.

378
00:28:49,841 --> 00:28:51,809
You...

379
00:28:51,943 --> 00:28:54,002
He's nearly dead, so I won't care.

380
00:28:54,178 --> 00:28:56,203
If not, maybe I will.

381
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:09,649
Hello?

382
00:29:09,794 --> 00:29:10,783
Ka-kui!

383
00:29:10,995 --> 00:29:12,360
May!

384
00:29:12,697 --> 00:29:13,959
You recognise her voice.

385
00:29:14,265 --> 00:29:16,130
We're at the Hung Fung Industrial Building.

386
00:29:16,501 --> 00:29:18,093
Who is this? What do you want?

387
00:29:18,603 --> 00:29:21,071
Come alone or she's dead.

388
00:29:21,506 --> 00:29:24,805
Wait!

389
00:29:26,177 --> 00:29:27,166
I know where it is.

390
00:30:03,047 --> 00:30:06,813
May! Are you all right?

391
00:30:10,254 --> 00:30:11,243
Be quiet.

392
00:30:11,522 --> 00:30:12,511
Are you all right?

393
00:30:12,690 --> 00:30:13,679
I'm OK.

394
00:30:13,858 --> 00:30:14,847
Why have you kidnapped her?

395
00:30:15,259 --> 00:30:18,023
Ka-kui, by the time you read
this letter...

396
00:30:18,229 --> 00:30:19,218
Stop!

397
00:30:19,363 --> 00:30:20,694
...I've decided we should be apart.

398
00:30:20,898 --> 00:30:21,887
No.

399
00:30:22,366 --> 00:30:24,800
I don't think I'll see you again.

400
00:30:25,336 --> 00:30:27,463
It's a love letter!

401
00:30:29,340 --> 00:30:32,434
Just like they say,
Unlucky in love, lucky in money.

402
00:30:32,677 --> 00:30:33,666
There's more.

403
00:30:33,778 --> 00:30:34,767
Bastard!

404
00:30:34,912 --> 00:30:38,939
When we met,
I thought you liked your job very much

405
00:30:39,217 --> 00:30:42,209
and you'd be my Mr Right.

406
00:30:42,453 --> 00:30:44,421
Now I realise the only thing

407
00:30:44,589 --> 00:30:47,251
that matters in your life is your work.

408
00:30:47,492 --> 00:30:51,428
I tell myself that what
made me fall in love with you

409
00:30:51,763 --> 00:30:55,358
is also what
made me want to leave you.

410
00:30:56,167 --> 00:30:58,567
Yeah, why? Why did you break up?

411
00:30:59,971 --> 00:31:03,498
You told me that

412
00:31:03,875 --> 00:31:05,069
you didn't want me involved with your work,

413
00:31:05,376 --> 00:31:06,400
but I didn't mind.

414
00:31:06,611 --> 00:31:09,307
You never spent
enough time with me.

415
00:31:09,514 --> 00:31:12,210
Being with you was
the happiest time in my life.

416
00:31:12,483 --> 00:31:14,348
But when you weren't there,

417
00:31:14,585 --> 00:31:17,952
it was the worst time of my life.

418
00:31:18,189 --> 00:31:19,417
That's not right.

419
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:21,820
If I didn't leave you,

420
00:31:22,126 --> 00:31:25,823
I'd spend my life waiting
for you to come home...

421
00:31:26,364 --> 00:31:28,093
Can't you stop it?!

422
00:31:31,702 --> 00:31:32,862
She's crying!

423
00:31:33,237 --> 00:31:34,226
So is he.

424
00:31:35,406 --> 00:31:36,395
Keep reading, go on.

425
00:31:37,875 --> 00:31:41,709
..because you can never stop
being a policeman.

426
00:31:42,079 --> 00:31:43,603
a policeman who never stops.

427
00:31:44,715 --> 00:31:45,807
We're in trouble.

428
00:31:46,617 --> 00:31:49,381
I think it's the right decision.

429
00:31:50,388 --> 00:31:54,848
Please forgive me for making
such a selfish choice, May.

430
00:31:59,831 --> 00:32:00,820
What do you want?

431
00:32:01,265 --> 00:32:03,733
We want you to help us get rich.

432
00:32:04,735 --> 00:32:07,169
Our speciality is blackmail

433
00:32:09,473 --> 00:32:12,169
and the hardest part of it is the pick up.

434
00:32:14,245 --> 00:32:15,769
You'll collect the ransom for us.

435
00:32:15,980 --> 00:32:16,969
No way!

436
00:32:17,315 --> 00:32:18,304
You don't have a choice.

437
00:32:18,816 --> 00:32:21,250
He said no.

438
00:32:29,694 --> 00:32:31,252
I think you'll enjoy this.

439
00:32:34,365 --> 00:32:35,354
Stop!

440
00:32:36,100 --> 00:32:38,295
Don't!

441
00:32:38,736 --> 00:32:40,465
Stop it! Please!

442
00:32:40,805 --> 00:32:44,138
Stop it!

443
00:32:44,408 --> 00:32:47,571
Please stop it!

444
00:32:48,679 --> 00:32:49,907
Ka-kui, are you hurt?

445
00:32:51,883 --> 00:32:52,872
Don't worry.

446
00:32:55,653 --> 00:32:56,813
So you want to play the hero?

447
00:33:15,439 --> 00:33:16,872
Now it's your turn.

448
00:33:29,487 --> 00:33:30,476
Please don't!

449
00:33:43,768 --> 00:33:44,757
You rotten swine!

450
00:33:47,038 --> 00:33:48,027
Nice one!

451
00:33:48,873 --> 00:33:49,862
Kill me if you have the guts.

452
00:33:50,107 --> 00:33:51,233
So tough!

453
00:33:51,709 --> 00:33:55,611
Really? Let's see if his girl
is tough, too.

454
00:33:58,516 --> 00:33:59,505
What do you want?

455
00:34:01,619 --> 00:34:08,787
How's that?! How's that?

456
00:34:09,727 --> 00:34:11,592
Enough! You've made your point.

457
00:34:13,097 --> 00:34:14,086
Does that mean you'll do it?

458
00:34:14,832 --> 00:34:17,596
Just let her go. I'll do anything.

459
00:34:17,768 --> 00:34:19,065
We won't let her go

460
00:34:19,337 --> 00:34:20,634
unless you help us.

461
00:34:21,238 --> 00:34:22,466
What do you want me to do?

462
00:34:22,673 --> 00:34:25,073
Collect the money for us.

463
00:34:26,344 --> 00:34:27,333
You don't have any choice.

464
00:34:37,321 --> 00:34:38,310
I'll do it.

465
00:34:38,622 --> 00:34:39,611
Good man.

466
00:35:03,948 --> 00:35:05,540
I wouldn't advise you to remove it.

467
00:35:06,317 --> 00:35:08,717
Break one wire and the whole thing blows.

468
00:35:10,054 --> 00:35:12,545
The same thing happens
if I press this button.

469
00:35:19,096 --> 00:35:21,223
You'd better be careful.

470
00:35:38,849 --> 00:35:39,838
Ka-kui.

471
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,809
Be careful.

472
00:35:45,256 --> 00:35:46,245
I'll come back for you.

473
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:03,929
Ready?

474
00:36:04,075 --> 00:36:05,064
He's on the line.

475
00:36:05,109 --> 00:36:06,098
Trace the call.

476
00:36:06,243 --> 00:36:07,232
I'll get Uncle Bill.

477
00:36:08,979 --> 00:36:09,968
Is the money ready?

478
00:36:10,014 --> 00:36:12,141
We'll collect it in 10 minutes.

479
00:36:12,650 --> 00:36:13,639
It's ready.

480
00:36:13,851 --> 00:36:14,840
Did you call the cops?

481
00:36:15,019 --> 00:36:16,008
No.

482
00:36:28,766 --> 00:36:29,755
Where's Ka-kui?

483
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:30,789
I can't find him.

484
00:36:31,535 --> 00:36:33,594
How could he be so irresponsible?

485
00:36:33,637 --> 00:36:34,626
I can't wait.

486
00:36:34,672 --> 00:36:36,572
Don't take any risks.

487
00:36:37,007 --> 00:36:37,996
Let's go.

488
00:36:46,117 --> 00:36:48,813
You'll have 10 minutes
to get back here again.

489
00:36:49,487 --> 00:36:50,579
No tricks.

490
00:36:50,988 --> 00:36:52,455
If we don't get our money,

491
00:36:52,957 --> 00:36:54,618
your vest will go bang!

492
00:36:56,494 --> 00:36:57,483
We'll be waiting.

493
00:36:59,196 --> 00:37:00,185
Get going.

494
00:37:05,336 --> 00:37:06,325
Good luck.

495
00:37:14,478 --> 00:37:15,467
Yes?

496
00:37:15,513 --> 00:37:16,502
Police officers.

497
00:37:19,583 --> 00:37:20,675
Mr. Fung Chairman

498
00:37:20,951 --> 00:37:21,940
You will pay me.

499
00:37:22,620 --> 00:37:24,019
How you know?

500
00:37:24,555 --> 00:37:25,544
Please sit.

501
00:37:27,491 --> 00:37:29,186
You promised to bug

502
00:37:30,995 --> 00:37:33,088
We could check it.

503
00:37:33,297 --> 00:37:35,094
It's bad that you aren't that effective
when handling the bomb case.

504
00:37:35,266 --> 00:37:36,255
We have everything ready.

505
00:37:36,333 --> 00:37:37,823
Once they pay the money,
we will have our action.

506
00:37:38,002 --> 00:37:40,095
Hope you won't do anything
to make anything worse.

507
00:37:40,337 --> 00:37:42,032
Because this will encourage the bombers.

508
00:37:42,306 --> 00:37:43,603
So they police couldn't help.

509
00:37:43,908 --> 00:37:45,239
We could only depend on ourselves.

510
00:37:51,215 --> 00:37:52,204
Ka-kui, the boss was looking...

511
00:37:52,249 --> 00:37:55,013
Ka-kui! It's Ka-kui.

512
00:37:55,586 --> 00:37:56,575
Ka-kui!

513
00:37:57,788 --> 00:37:59,153
Ka-kui! Out of my way.

514
00:37:59,790 --> 00:38:02,520
Let me go!

515
00:38:03,294 --> 00:38:05,285
Get out of my way!

516
00:38:07,064 --> 00:38:08,861
Ka-kui!

517
00:38:11,635 --> 00:38:12,624
Excuse me.

518
00:38:16,373 --> 00:38:17,362
Ka-kui.

519
00:38:18,042 --> 00:38:19,270
Ka-kui, where have you been?

520
00:38:19,543 --> 00:38:21,943
Never mind. I'm here to collect the money.

521
00:38:22,379 --> 00:38:23,368
What?!

522
00:38:23,581 --> 00:38:24,570
Is he your man?

523
00:38:24,615 --> 00:38:25,582
Yes, he is.

524
00:38:25,616 --> 00:38:26,776
Ka-kui, what's going on?

525
00:38:27,384 --> 00:38:30,444
We don't have much time. The money!

526
00:38:38,562 --> 00:38:39,551
What are you doing?

527
00:38:39,597 --> 00:38:40,188
Ka-kui!

528
00:38:40,231 --> 00:38:42,358
Move and I'll shoot you.

529
00:38:42,733 --> 00:38:43,859
Don't pull the trigger.

530
00:38:45,269 --> 00:38:46,258
No!

531
00:38:46,503 --> 00:38:47,492
Don't push me.

532
00:38:48,739 --> 00:38:51,606
If you shoot me, everybody here...

533
00:38:52,509 --> 00:38:53,737
will be blown sky high.

534
00:38:57,948 --> 00:39:00,075
If one wire breaks,
the whole thing will explode.

535
00:39:01,252 --> 00:39:02,981
Ka-kui, what's going on?

536
00:39:03,254 --> 00:39:05,051
Can't we work this out?

537
00:39:05,256 --> 00:39:07,417
If I don't leave here in 10 minutes,
it will go off.

538
00:39:07,758 --> 00:39:09,419
I don't have time!

539
00:39:22,406 --> 00:39:23,395
Let him go. Please leave us.

540
00:39:28,178 --> 00:39:29,167
Attention all units,

541
00:39:29,546 --> 00:39:31,070
don't stop Ka-kui.

542
00:39:42,793 --> 00:39:44,283
Ka-kui...

543
00:39:44,561 --> 00:39:45,550
Don't follow me.

544
00:39:47,464 --> 00:39:50,558
Ka-kui...

545
00:39:50,734 --> 00:39:51,723
Get out of my way!

546
00:40:03,647 --> 00:40:04,636
I think he did it.

547
00:40:04,682 --> 00:40:05,671
Great.

548
00:40:07,518 --> 00:40:08,507
Looks like he was followed.

549
00:40:08,552 --> 00:40:09,541
Let's go.

550
00:40:34,445 --> 00:40:35,537
Tell him to move up.

551
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:44,609
Give me the money.

552
00:40:44,655 --> 00:40:47,317
I'm being followed.
Let me shake them off first.

553
00:40:48,158 --> 00:40:49,147
Believe me.

554
00:40:58,369 --> 00:40:59,358
Are the cops behind us?

555
00:41:09,813 --> 00:41:10,973
Stay back! Don't come near.

556
00:41:21,725 --> 00:41:22,851
Why did you stop here?

557
00:41:28,399 --> 00:41:29,889
What are you doing?

558
00:41:29,967 --> 00:41:30,956
What's going on?

559
00:41:31,001 --> 00:41:32,593
A bomb's about to blow. Run!

560
00:41:33,137 --> 00:41:34,764
A bomb! Run!

561
00:41:55,459 --> 00:41:56,448
There's no cops!

562
00:41:56,593 --> 00:41:58,151
I'll blow him to bits.

563
00:41:58,429 --> 00:42:00,454
Wait! What about the money?

564
00:42:00,964 --> 00:42:03,398
And you can't get a radio signal
in the tunnel.

565
00:42:03,801 --> 00:42:04,790
What now?

566
00:42:04,835 --> 00:42:06,996
We've got the girl. Don't worry.
Let's go.

567
00:42:07,237 --> 00:42:08,226
Maybe we should split up.

568
00:43:44,902 --> 00:43:45,891
Kill her if it goes wrong.

569
00:44:46,430 --> 00:44:47,419
May.

570
00:44:54,171 --> 00:44:55,229
Where is she?

571
00:45:17,861 --> 00:45:18,850
Look, he's back.

572
00:45:24,001 --> 00:45:25,525
I told you he wouldn't play tricks.

573
00:45:48,091 --> 00:45:49,080
May!

574
00:45:55,265 --> 00:45:56,254
Quiet.

575
00:46:05,942 --> 00:46:08,035
Freeze! You're under arrest.

576
00:46:09,179 --> 00:46:11,010
Really?

577
00:46:11,548 --> 00:46:13,311
Come on then, arrest us.

578
00:46:13,884 --> 00:46:14,873
Don't move.

579
00:46:15,686 --> 00:46:16,675
Move and I'll shoot you.

580
00:46:18,689 --> 00:46:21,180
You think so? You'd have to shoot fast.

581
00:46:21,792 --> 00:46:22,986
There are three of us.

582
00:46:23,860 --> 00:46:24,849
Think about it.

583
00:46:24,895 --> 00:46:26,920
If I don't shoot you,
you'll only spend years in jail.

584
00:46:27,164 --> 00:46:28,188
And then you'll be a reformed person.

585
00:46:28,532 --> 00:46:29,999
That's better than dying in this condition.

586
00:46:33,103 --> 00:46:34,092
We are ready.

587
00:46:34,971 --> 00:46:36,199
We want to be rich.

588
00:46:36,440 --> 00:46:37,737
Yes.

589
00:46:38,375 --> 00:46:39,933
But you are way too cruel.

590
00:46:40,177 --> 00:46:42,304
What is cruel?
Fortune Maker

591
00:46:42,479 --> 00:46:44,811
In this society,
only if you do something good to the society,

592
00:46:45,115 --> 00:46:47,276
everyone will help you.
You will be repaid.

593
00:46:47,417 --> 00:46:48,406
Then you will be rich.

594
00:46:50,487 --> 00:46:52,717
And you will have new outlook.
That's what you could do.

595
00:46:53,090 --> 00:46:54,216
Yet, now what you have done,

596
00:46:54,458 --> 00:46:55,823
has harmed the society.

597
00:46:56,126 --> 00:46:57,115
This is against everyone's benefit.

598
00:46:57,427 --> 00:46:58,792
What does that mean?

599
00:46:58,862 --> 00:46:59,851
Look.

600
00:46:59,896 --> 00:47:00,658
Beside you guys,

601
00:47:00,697 --> 00:47:01,789
who will think you are doing the right thing?

602
00:47:01,998 --> 00:47:03,295
Who would think of your purpose?

603
00:47:06,336 --> 00:47:07,530
You are right.

604
00:47:08,105 --> 00:47:11,597
Yes.

605
00:47:12,509 --> 00:47:13,533
That doesn't sound too bad,

606
00:47:13,777 --> 00:47:16,211
we might take your advice.

607
00:47:17,013 --> 00:47:18,071
But we're still young.

608
00:47:18,749 --> 00:47:20,114
After we did our time, we'd all be old men.

609
00:47:22,519 --> 00:47:23,508
Don't push me!

610
00:47:23,720 --> 00:47:25,688
Run! This is a fireworks factory.

611
00:49:48,632 --> 00:49:49,621
May!

612
00:49:49,666 --> 00:49:50,655
I'm over here!

613
00:49:51,468 --> 00:49:52,457
Are you all right?

614
00:49:59,509 --> 00:50:00,737
Ka-kui, be careful!

615
00:50:24,567 --> 00:50:25,556
Good work!

616
00:50:35,211 --> 00:50:36,200
Ka-kui! Come here!

617
00:50:36,313 --> 00:50:37,302
There's the rubbish chute.

618
00:50:50,727 --> 00:50:51,716
There's an exit.

619
00:50:54,631 --> 00:50:55,620
May, you go first.

620
00:51:02,072 --> 00:51:03,061
It looks too high.

621
00:51:03,573 --> 00:51:04,972
Just jump.

622
00:51:26,496 --> 00:51:27,485
Ka-kui, are you all right?

623
00:51:29,299 --> 00:51:31,665
I'm fine. Get out of here, May.
As far as you can.

624
00:51:31,868 --> 00:51:32,857
Be careful.

625
00:53:48,204 --> 00:53:49,228
Dad.

626
00:53:49,439 --> 00:53:51,600
Do you want to try this yourself?

627
00:53:51,875 --> 00:53:53,672
You want some more? Take this.

628
00:53:55,044 --> 00:53:56,136
And more, bastard.

629
00:53:56,346 --> 00:53:57,973
Want some more?

630
00:53:58,348 --> 00:54:00,578
You want some more? Here!

631
00:54:01,684 --> 00:54:07,645
Bastard!

632
00:54:07,957 --> 00:54:14,795
More?

633
00:54:55,271 --> 00:54:56,260
Shit. Not enough...

634
00:55:44,387 --> 00:55:45,718
Ka-kui!

635
00:55:55,098 --> 00:55:56,087
Stop crying, OK?

636
00:55:57,200 --> 00:55:59,691
Look, the fireworks are beautiful.
